VoiceList.Entry: “…and they told me I would be staying at five star hotels on these trips…”
Shinra Manager “How can you guys sleep in a place like this?”
Shinra Manager “I only came to help transport the Sister Ray from Junon…”
“But now the company says don't bother coming back…”
“Is this what happens to a loyal Shinra man?”
“If Weapon killed all the upper management… then I'll be President!!”
